  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "recruitment agent",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for an independent and responsible Overseas Student Recruitment Agent to support BizChamp International College in reaching potential students from overseas markets. The agent will introduce our diploma and postgraduate programmes to suitable candidates and assist them through the enquiry and application process.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>This is an independent, commission-based role and does not involve teaching or delivering training.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities</p>\n<p>\t•\tPromote BizChamp International College programmes to potential students from overseas</p>\n<p>\t•\tProvide accurate course information and explain entry requirements, fees, and study schedules</p>\n<p>\t•\tGuide interested applicants through enquiry, document submission, and registration steps</p>\n<p>\t•\tMaintain clear communication with students and BizChamp admin team</p>\n<p>\t•\tEnsure all student information submitted is accurate and complete</p>\n<p>\t•\tUphold professional conduct and follow BizChamp’s internal policies and SSG/CPE regulations</p>\n<p>\t•\tBuild and maintain relationships with overseas partners, parents, and referral networks</p>\n<p>\t•\tSubmit weekly updates on student leads and conversions</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Working Arrangement</p>\n<p>\t•\tIndependent / Part-time role</p>\n<p>\t•\tCommission-based earnings</p>\n<p>\t•\tFlexible working hours</p>\n<p>\t•\tTraining on course information will be provided</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>About BizChamp International College</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>BizChamp International College is a private education institution in Singapore offering diploma and postgraduate diploma programmes for working adults and international learners. We are committed to delivering quality education and supporting our students throughout their academic journey.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Work Location / 工作地点</p>\n<p>116 Middle Road, #04-02, ICB Enterprise House, Singapore 188972</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Employment Type / 职位类型</p>\n<p>Part-Time / 兼职</p>",
